What is the projected market size & growth rate of the Laryngoscopes Market?

Market Analysis and Size

The rising prevalence of laryngeal cancers, infections, and chronic respiratory diseases is a main factor that enhances market growth. Globally, the lifetime risk of developing laryngeal cancer is around 1 in 190 for men and 1 in 830 for women. Furthermore, increasing awareness of the benefits of using modern laryngoscopes over traditional laryngoscopes is contributing to market growth.

Data Bridge Market Research analyzes that the global laryngoscopes market, which was USD 760.32 million in 2022, would rocket up to USD 1459.68 million by 2030, and is expected to undergo a CAGR of 8.50% during the forecast period. “Flexible” dominates the type segment of the market owing to the high demand for this type.

